&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Cognism is looking for an SEO &amp;amp; AEO Manager to help improve our organic visibility across traditional search, AI search, and LLM-driven discovery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is suited to someone with strong technical SEO foundations, a commercial mindset, and the ability to balance technical optimisation with high-quality content creation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
