&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Content is a key part of this role, but this is not a content manager position. You will need to create, brief, edit, and optimise content, while also owning the SEO and AEO strategy behind it. The focus is on producing content that performs: content that ranks, answers buyer questions, strengthens Cognism’s authority, supports demand generation, and drives qualified traffic, conversions, pipeline, and revenue.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
